Paper: hep-th/9909106

Date: 1999-09-15

Title: Oscillating Inflation with a non-minimally coupled scalar field

Authors: Jae-weon Lee,Seoktae Koh,Chanyong Park,Sang Jin Sin and Chul H. Lee

Comments: 9 pages, 1 figure, to be published in PRD

Journal-ref: Phys.Rev. D61 (2000) 027301

The oscillating inflation model recently proposed by Damour and Mukhanov isinvestigated with a non-minimal coupling. Numerical study confirms aninflationary behavior and the density perturbation is obtained. A successfulinflation requires the gravity-dilaton coupling to be small.